            "question_1": "1. Will these turn green or tarnish?",
            "answer_1": "<p>Oxidised jewellery has an intentionally darkened finish — it is not plated silver that fades. With basic care (keeping dry, storing properly) these maintain their look for a long time.</p>",
            "question_2": "2.Are these suitable for sensitive ears?",
            "answer_2": "<p>The hooks and posts are smooth and standard gauge. Most customers wear them without issues. If you have highly sensitive ears, we recommend wearing for a few hours first.</p>",
            "question_3": "3.Can I buy individual earrings from this set?",
            "answer_3": "<p>The Rang Mahal Collection is available only as a complete set of 16</p>",
            "question_4": "4.How is the packaging?",
            "answer_4": "<p>All 16 pairs come beautifully packed in a premium Adhya gift box, perfect for gifting or treating yourself. Designed to carry and protect your earrings, keeping them safe from damage.</p>",
            "question_5": "5.What if one earring arrives damaged?",
            "answer_5": "<p>We check every pair before dispatch. If anything arrives damaged, reach out to us within 48 hours with a photo and we'll make it right.</p>"
